# sessionDidRunDeferredStart(_:)

**Instance Method**

This method gets called by the session when deferred start has finished running.

## Declaration

```swift
func sessionDidRunDeferredStart(_ session: AVCaptureSession)
```

## Parameters

- **session**: The [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVCaptureSession] instance that runs the deferred start.

## Responding to deferred start events

- **sessionWillRunDeferredStart(_:)**: This method gets called by the session when deferred start is about to run.
